## Scenarios

### S1: First Call — Insufficient Info

```
Input:  { intent: "加 OAuth2", project_id: "myapp", clarifications: [] }
Agent:  search specs → finds AuthProvider trait spec
        analyze → missing: which providers? refresh? integrate existing?
Output: { type: "need_clarification", questions: [
          { id: "q1", question: "需要支援哪些 OAuth2 provider?", why: "影響拆分多少實作 issue", suggestions: ["Google", "GitHub", "Microsoft"] },
          { id: "q2", question: "需要 token refresh 嗎?", why: "影響 middleware 設計" }
        ]}
```

### S2: With Clarifications — Produce Issues

```
Input:  { intent: "加 OAuth2", project_id: "myapp", clarifications: [
          { question: "需要支援哪些 provider?", answer: "Google + GitHub" },
          { question: "需要 token refresh 嗎?", answer: "要" }
        ]}
Agent:  search specs → finds AuthProvider, SessionMiddleware specs
        analyze → sufficient info
Output: { type: "create_issues", issues: [
          { title: "feat(auth): add OAuth2Provider trait", priority: "P1", depends_on: [], ... },
          { title: "feat(auth): implement Google OAuth2", priority: "P1", depends_on: ["OAuth2Provider trait"], ... },
          { title: "feat(auth): implement GitHub OAuth2", priority: "P1", depends_on: ["OAuth2Provider trait"], ... }
        ], summary: "3 issues: 1 trait + 2 provider 實作" }
```

### S3: Simple Intent — No Clarification Needed

```
Input:  { intent: "fix: login button 404 on /auth/callback", project_id: "myapp", clarifications: [] }
Agent:  search specs → finds auth routing spec
        analyze → clear enough (bug with specific path)
Output: { type: "create_issues", issues: [
          { title: "fix(auth): login callback returns 404", issue_type: "bug", priority: "P0", ... }
        ], summary: "1 bug fix issue" }
```

### S4: No Specs Found

```
Input:  { intent: "加一個新的 payment module", project_id: "myapp", clarifications: [] }
Agent:  search specs → no relevant specs found
        analyze → new domain, need full requirements
Output: { type: "need_clarification", questions: [
          { id: "q1", question: "Payment 需要支援哪些支付方式?", why: "沒有找到相關 spec，需要從頭定義" },
          { id: "q2", question: "需要支援退款流程嗎?", why: "影響 state machine 複雜度" }
        ]}
```
